data.description: GREAT NEWS! This property qualifies for a 100% LTV mortgage with no Mortgage Insurance for owner-occupants. No income limits but must have a credit score of 620 or more! Ask me for more information if interested! ........ Spacious, convenient, and affordable, this 3-bedroom home has an open concept on the 1st floor, an eat-in kitchen, and a nice-sized patio. Upstairs, you'll find a unique layout with a spacious hallway, a large front bedroom, a great rear office, and a center bedroom with a skylight. The main bathroom is beautifully updated with a shower stall. The 2nd bathroom is in the unfinished basement and is perfect for a dog washing station or showering after a hard day's work with your hands. So many updates too: new heater, soil line, gas dryer, and chimney! The roof was new in 2019, before the Seller's ownership. A 10-minute walk gets you to Passyunk Ave retail & restaurants or Dickenson Square Park. A 10-minute drive gets you to I95, I76 and Center City.  Schedule your visit today!
